Package: FibFreq
Type: Package
Title: Frequency Estimation for Essentially Periodic Time Series 
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Annette Witt with support of Holger Nobach and Laura Diaz-Maue, Data are provided by Laura Diaz-Maue
Maintainer: Annette Witt <annette.witt@med.uni-goettingen.de>
Description: The Package 'FibFreq' contains four frequency estimation functions which are appropriate for essentially periodoc time series 
    such as the sunspot data or ecg data of fibrillating hearts.
    Also, it provides a data set of 117 murine optical cardiograms.
    They are published here: LD, HN, AW: xxx. Journal of yyy, 2024. 
